PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?dog ?age WHERE {
  ?dog wdt:P31 wd:Q144 ; wdt:P569 ?birthDate ; wdt:P570 ?deathDate .
  BIND( ( year( ?deathDate ) - year( ?birthDate ) ) AS ?age )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?age )
LIMIT 2

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?discipline ?label WHERE {
  ?discipline wdt:P31 wd:Q11081 ; rdfs:label ?label .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?label ) = 'de' ) FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?label ) , 'linguistik' ) )
}

  ?book wdt:P50 ?author .
